    <article>
        <h2>Community-based Boatbuilding on Little Cranberry Island, Maine</h2>
        <p>More than just boatbuilding, we serve as a <a href="#">community hub</a> providing a place for all ages to gather, to share, and to learn throughout the year.</p>
