    <article>
        <a href="#" class="img-caption" data-tooltip="Since 2006 we've launched 15 boats. Launch day is always a fun community celebration."><img src="/static/images/story-launch.jpg"></a>
        <p>Each summer we <a href="#">launch a new boat</a>, built with the combined efforts of our island’s kids and adults. From supporting the working waterfront, providing access to our waterways, to preserving local history, all of our boats serve the community in some way.</p>
        {# <a href="#">Our Boats</a> #}
    </article>
    <article>
